0706.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536059-20200706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96Fi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=3fc4720b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536059-20200706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e2080aaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536059-20200706.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「保就業」計劃公布第三批僱主名單，涉及約3萬名僱主及逾33萬名受薪僱員，工資補貼額合共約77億元。<br />\n<br />\n有過百間獲批資助公司的承諾受薪僱員人數為0，部分公司申領金額超過10萬元，包括「聯向企業有限公司」、「時信專業服務有限公司」及「本草唯物」。<br />\n<br />\n至於申領最高金額的是「中原地產代理有限公司 」，涉及1億1500多萬元，承諾受薪僱員總數為5600多人；<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">電視廣播有限公司</span></span></strong>申領8500多萬元，涉及3100多名僱員；美聯商業管理有限公司申領6300多萬元，涉及3100多名員工。<br />\n<br />\n零售業方面，周大福珠寶金行有限公司申領 7700多萬元，涉及2800多名員工；莎莎化妝品有限公司申領5900多萬元，承諾受薪僱員數目為2100多人。"},{"pid":"1dc13ce84c61dcae5b20a9124570edc21fc284a5","tid":2096244,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"中原唔係炒人咩？"},{"pid":"f3dec0a306860e151c23a1d983285bd2a224a4aa","tid":2096244,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"唔怪得施永狗近排咁落力"},{"pid":"3219bfd60c118cfe166dc552f3797d0bda98540a","tid":2096244,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"個機制根本垃圾"}],"pinned":{"pid":"7d0bb71022060e4879d5f9f36828cfd43d9fed1c","tid":2096244,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"施生：我係賺錢，但我係要拎呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://paper.hket.com/article/2615065/代理自僱工作%20工資補貼恐難受惠\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2615065%2F%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E8%87%AA%E5%83%B1%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%2520%E5%B7%A5%E8%B3%87%E8%A3%9C%E8%B2%BC%E6%81%90%E9%9B%A3%E5%8F%97